tafsir[34]{c,v,t}:
  31,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: yewtere sugu Й—ee Aayeeje yawtiino ka fuЙ—Й—orde cortewol Al-Baqarah."
  31,2,"ЖҠee Aayeeje jippinaaЙ—e Й— maaЙ—a an NulaaЙ—o, ko Aayeeje Deftere yewtaynde hikma."
  31,3,"Ko nde peewal e yurmeende wonannde moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e golle Й“en, tottugol Й“e haqqeeji Joomi maЙ“Й“e e jeyaaЙ“e Alla Й—in."
  31,4,"ЖҒen ГұinnirooЙ“e julde nden no timmiri, Й“e yaltina asakal jawle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e yananaaЙ“e fii ko woni ka laakara kon, immorde e ummital, e hasbeede, e warjeede e lepteede."
  31,5,"ЖҒen siforiiЙ“e Й—in sifaaji, ko Й“en woni e peewal immorde e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“en kadi woni malirayЙ“e heЙ“ugol ko Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“unoo, e daЙ—ugol ko Й“e hulunoo."
  31,6,"Hino woodi e yimЙ“e Й“en, nanndo An-NaД‘r ibn al-ДҰГўrith, suЙ“otooЙ“e haalaaji mbeleeЙ—e ko yiilira yimЙ“e Й“en e diina Alla kan, ko aldaa e ganndal, O jogitora Aayeeje Alla Й—en jalnori. ЖҒen siforaaЙ“e Й—in sifaaji, hino woodani Й“e lepte hoynooje ka laakara."
  31,7,"Si Aayeeje Amen Й—en janngaama e makko, o huccitira townitanagol nanugol Й—e, wa si tawii o nanaali Й—e, wa si tawii ko pahu woni e noppi makko. Weltinir-mo an NulaaЙ—o, lepte muusuЙ—e habbtiiЙ—e mo."
  31,8,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi Й—in, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji neema. ЖҒe neeminoray e majji ko Alla maraniЙ“e kon ton."
  31,9,"Ko Й“e duumotooЙ“e nder ton. Alla fodiriiЙ“e Й—um fodoore gonnga nde sikke alaa e m'un. Ko Kanko woni FooluЙ—o Mo fooletaake, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e tagu Mun, e toppitagol Mun e sari'a Mun."
  31,10,"Alla seniiЙ—o On tagirii kammuuli Й—in toownaaЙ—i ko aldaa e tugaale, O waЙ—i pelle tabituЙ—e ka leydi fii wata Й—e dillin on, O saakiti e mayri kala noone e kulle. Men jippiniri ka kammu ndiyam, Men fuЙ—iniri leydi ndin kala noone e tutateeri yooЙ—uЙ—i, ko yimЙ“e e daabeeji nafitora."
  31,11,"Ko jantaa koo, ko tagu Alla. Hollee Lam onon sirkooЙ“e Й“en, ko honЙ—um Й—in rewton gaanin Alla tagi? Si ko woni, tooГұuЙ“e Й“en no e majjere Й“anngunde, tawde Й“e kafidii Joomi maЙ“Й“e e tagaaЙ—i Й—i tagataa hay huunde."
  31,12,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Luqmaana faamu diina e anndangol piiji Й—in. Men wi'ani mo: Ko an yo Luqmaan, yettu ko Alla neeminir-maahawridine e Й—oftagol Mo ngol. Kala yettuЙ—o Joomi mun, haray nafa mun on ko e makko ruttitoo, Alla kan ko yonndiniiЙ—o e yettoore makko; kala non yedduЙ—o neemaaji Alla Й—in e dow mun, haray lorra yeddugol mo ngol, ko e makko yiltotoo, o lorotaa Alla huunde e Й—um, Alla ko Galo yonndiniiЙ—o e tagu Makko ngun fow, YettiniiЙ—o e kala fiyaaku."
  31,13,"Janto an NulaaЙ—o, tuma Luqmaana wi'annoo geЙ—al makko on, hari himo rerЙ—ina mo e moЖҙЖҙere, o rentina mo e bone: Ko an yo Й“inngel am, wata a kafidu e Alla goЙ—Й—um goo. Pellet, kafidugol Alla goЙ—Й—um goo ka dewal, ko tooГұe mawЙ—e, wonande wonkii faggitiiki on bakkaatu Й“urЙ—o mawnude, luttinoowo e Yiite."
  31,14,"Men yamirii neЙ—Й—anke on, Й—oftagol jinnaaЙ“e makko Й“en e kala ko yeddugol Alla alaa e mu'un. Yumma makko saawirii mo ka reedu mun, tampere e hoore tampere. Entugol mon ngol, ko e nder duuЙ“i Й—iЙ—i. Men wi'ani mo: Yettu Alla e ko O neemini kon e maaЙ—a, hooti annditanaa jinnaaЙ“e maa Й“en e ko Й“e tampidi e ne'ugol ma toppito maa kon. Ko ka An tun woni ruttorde nden, Mi yoЙ“ita kala e ko hanndi kon."
  31,15,"Si jinnaaЙ“e maa Й“en etike fawugol sirkangol Alla, wata a Й—ofto Й“e e Й—um; tawde Й—oftagol alanaa tagaaЙ—o, e yeddugol taguЙ—o On. Wonndir e maЙ“Й“e ka aduna Й—oo, Й—iggere, e jokkagol Й“e moЖҙЖҙoo e maЙ“Й“e. Jokku laawol on ruttiiЙ—o faade e tawhiidi e Й—oftaare. Refti ko ka An tun, woni ruttorde mon on fow, Г‘alnde Darngal. Mi humpitoya on ko gollaynoЙ—on kon aduna, Mi yoЙ“ita on Й—um."
  31,16,"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, anndu bone maa moЖҙЖҙere, no nde fanЙ—iri woo, si nde fotii wa abbere, immorde e nenndi foГұГұe, nde wona e nder fetere, hara ndi yi'otaako, maa nde wona e nooku woo ka kammuuli maa ka leydi, annndu pellet, Alla artiroyay nde Г‘alnde Darngal, O yoЙ“ita jeyaaЙ—o on e mayre. Pellet, Alla ko NewiiЙ—o, huunde wirnanaaki Mo. Ko O humpitiiЙ—o kadi fii kala huunde e nokku mayre."
  31,17,"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, ГұiiЙ“nir julde nden tottirgol nde no timmiri, yamiraa moЖҙЖҙere, haЙ—aa ЕӢiГұere, muГұГұo-Й—aa e tampere ko heЙ“u-maa e Й—um. Pellet, ko yamira-Й—aa koo, ko jeyaaЙ—um e mawЙ—i Й—i Alla yamir-maa gollugol, a alaa ko suЙ“o-Й—aa e Й—um."
  31,18,"Wata a fal yeeso maa ngon e yimЙ“e Й“en townitaa- re, wata a yahru ka hoore leydi ГұaaЖҙagol mantoo. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa kala ГұaaЖҙoowo e yahdu mun, mantoroowo neemaaji mun, townitoo e yimЙ“e Й“en, hara o yettirtaa Й—i Alla."
  31,19,"Hakidnor e yahdu-maa ndun hakkunde yaawugol e nennorgol, joltinaa hito maa ngon, hara a towniraali ngo lorrugol. Anndu ko Й“uraa aГұeede e hitooji Й—in, pellet, ko luukaadu mbabba, sabu ko nba toowi hito kon."
  31,20,"E on yi'aali, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, wonnde Alla newianii on nafitorgol ko woni ka kammuuli kon, immorde e naange, e lewru e koode, O newinani on kadi ko woni ka leydi kon, immorde e daabeeji, e leЙ—Й—e e puЙ—i. O timminnirani on neemaaji Makko Й“annguЙ—i, wano labeede maa moЖҙЖҙude mbaadi, e neemaaji suuЙ—iiЙ—i, wano haqqil e ganndal. E hoore ko Й—in neemaaji woodi kon fow, hino woodi e yimЙ“e Й“en, wennjiroowo fii wootinЙ—ingol Alla, ko aldaa e tuuginagol e ganndal wahayu, immorde ka Alla, maa haqqil ndayginorki, wanaa fere Deftere Й“anngunde, jippiniraande ka Alla."
  31,21,"Si Й“ee wennjooЙ“e fii wooЙ—indingol Alla ngol wi'anaama: ""Jokkee wahayu mo Alla jippini on e NulaaЙ—o Makko on"", Й“e wi'ay: ""Men jokkataa Й—um. Wurin ko ko men tawri baabiraaЙ“e amen Й“en kon, e rewugol sanamu, men jokka"". E hara Й“e jokkay baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en, hay si tawii seytaane woniino noddiroowo Й“en e ko rewugol sanamuuji majjinayЙ—i Й“e, Й—i Й—owira e lepte Yiite dulЙ“oowe ngen Г‘alnde Darngal?"
  31,22,"Kala fewtirЙ—o e Alla, o laЙ“Й“inani Mo dewe Й—en, o moЖҙЖҙini golle makko Й—en, gomЙ—ii haray o jogitike ko Й“uri hoolnaade e ko jortiiЙ—o daЙ—al jogitotoo, tawde o hulaa nde Й—um taЖҙata. Awa ko faade ka Alla tun, woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in, O yoЙ“ita gooto kala e hanndi."
  31,23,"Kala yedduЙ—o Alla, wata keeferaaku makko sunine suninean NulaaЙ—o. Ko ka Amen tun, woni ruttorde maЙ“Й“e Г‘alnde Darngal, Men humpita Й“e ko huuwunoo e bonЙ—i ka aduna, Men yoЙ“ita Й“e Й—um. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o ko woni e fondooji Й“erЙ—e. Huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—um."
  31,24,"Men dakmitiray Й“e ko Men okki Й“en kon e dakamme aduna, yeru seeЙ—a tun, refti Men jooГұiroya Й“e e lepte saЙ—tuЙ—e Г‘alnde Darngal, Й—en woni lepte Yiite."
  31,25,"Pellet, si an NulaaЙ—o, a lamndike Й“ee sirkooЙ“e: ""Ko hommbo tagi kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin?"" Ma Й“e wi'u: ""Ko Alla tagi Й—i!"" Maakan Й“e: ""Yettoore woodani Alla feeГұinЙ—o hujja on e mon!"". Kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, sabu majjere maЙ“Й“e nden, Й“e anndaa hannduЙ—o e yettoore."
  31,26,"Ko Alla tun woodani tagu, e laamu e toppitagol kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Pellet, Alla, ko Kano woni YondiniiЙ—o e tagu Makko ngun fow, YettiniiЙ—o aduna e laakara."
  31,27,"Hay si tawii leЙ—Й—e ko woni ka hoore leydi kon fow, settiraama karambi, maayo ngon waЙ—taa ndaha, ngon Й“eydiraa maaje jeeЙ—iЙ—i, konnguЙ—i Alla Й—in lannataa, tawde wanaa ko lannata. Pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o Mo gooto foolataa, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o e tagu Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  31,28,"Tagugol on, onon Й“ee yimЙ“e, e immintingol on Г‘alnde Darngal fii hasbeede yoЙ“ee, wonaali, si wanaa wa tagugol fittaandu wooturu, immintinira ndu no newori. Pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo, Mo nanugol hito goo, haЙ—ataa Mo nanude hito woo. Ko O Yi'oowo, Mo yi'ugol goЙ—Й—um goo, haЙ—ataa Mo yi'ude huunde woo. Ko wano non kadi woniri, tagugol maa immintingol wonkii woo, ronkinirtaa Mo fii wonkii goo."
  31,29,"E a yi'aali wonnde Alla no Й—uytira jemma on fii Й“eydugol Гұalorma on, O Й—uytira kadi Гұalorma on fii Й“eydugol jemma on, O eЙ“Й“i dogudu naange ngen e lewru ndun, tawde gootel kala e majji no dogirde taarorde mun haa e dumunna happaaЙ—o? E wonnde All ko HumpitiiЙ—o ko golloton kon: huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e golle mon, O yoЙ“itoyay on e Й—um."
  31,30,"Ngool toppitagol e eЙ“Й“ugol, hino seeditoo wonnde ko Alla tun woni Goonga. Ko O Goonga e Jaati Makko, e Sifaaji Makko e Golle Makko. E wonnde pellet, ko sirkooЙ“e Й“en rewata kon gaanin Alla, Й—um ko meere nde tuugaaki hay e nokku. E wonnde pellet, Alla, ko Kanko woni ToowirЙ—o hoore tagu Makko ngun, Jaati Makko, e Mbaadi Makko e Kattal Makko. On Mo tawata, alaa ko toowi Й“uri Mo, On MawnuЙ—o Й“uri kala huunde."
  31,31,"E a yi'aali wonnde laaЙ—e Й—en hino dogira ka maayo e neweende Makko, fii yo O hollu on, onon yimЙ“e Й“en, yoga e dalilaaji tindinЙ—i kattal e neweende Makko. Wonii e Й—um, maandeeji tinndinЙ—i kattal Makko, woannde kala muГұГұotooЙ—o e lorra heЙ“oowo mo, yettoowo neema."
  31,32,"Si tawii morlooЙ—e Й—en huuЙ“irii Й“e kala bannge, wa'ii wa pelle maa duule, Й“e nodday Alla tun, Й“e laЙ“Й“inana Mo dewal e toraare; tuma nde O jaabinani Й“e, O daЙ—ndi Й“e yoolagol, O naЙ“iri Й“e ka njorndi, tawi no e maЙ“Й“e hakindiiЙ—o: mo waЙ—aali ko waЙ—Й—ii mo kon e yettugol neema on no haaniri, woЙ—Й“e goo yeddi neema on few. Awa yeddataa Aayeeje Amen Й—en, - si wanaa kala heewuЙ—o janfa, sifa on ahodunooЙ—o e Alla, wonnde pellet, si O danЙ—ndii mo, o tawete e yettooЙ“e Mo Й“en -, dullanoowo neemaaji Alla Й—in, mo yettataa Joomi mun e neema Makko on."
  31,33,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Hulee Joomi mon, Й—oftoЙ—on yamirooje Makko, woЙ—Й—itoЙ—on haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko. Hulon kadi lepte Гұalaande, nde baaba duncanoytaa Й“iЙ—Й—o mun, wanaa Й“iЙ—Й—o on kadi duncanoyta ben mun hay huunde. Pellet, fodoore Alla nden yoЙ“itugol Г‘alnde Darngal, ko nde tabitunde, feere mun alaa. Wata on jaЙ“u nguurdam aduna e welii-fotii majjam hoda on, wata seytaane hodir on ko Alla muГұГұori on kon leelnugol leptude on."
  31,34,"Pellet, ko ka Alla tun woni anndal Darnagl: Himo anndi nde darotoo, Himo jippina toЙ“o nde O haaji. Himo annda kadi ko woni ka nder renngaaji, ko deyel kaa ko gorel? Ka malkisaaЙ—o kaa ko malaaЙ—o? Wonkii woo anndaa ko faggitoo janngo, immorde e moЖҙЖҙere maa bone, wonkii woo kadi anndaa ko e leydi honndi maayata, ko Alla heeranii anndugol Й—um fow. Pellet, Alla ko AnnduЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o Й—um fow: huunde suuЙ—aaki Mo e Й—um."
